<text id="02-output-contract" title="Framework Decomposition Patterns Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the per-file decomposition report. Each fat file targeted for extraction emits a report; the report gates the actual refactor PR.</summary>

  <section title="JSON Schema (draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/framework-decomposition-patterns.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["artefact_id", "file_path", "framework", "file_type", "current_loc", "proposed_pattern", "target_loc", "coverage_or_plan", "verdict", "version", "last_reviewed"],
  "properties": {
    "artefact_id":     {"type": "string", "pattern": "^fdp-[a-z0-9-]{6,}$"},
    "file_path":       {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
    "framework":       {"enum": ["django", "rails", "laravel", "react", "nextjs", "generic"]},
    "file_type":       {"enum": ["view", "controller", "model", "component", "route", "service", "form"]},
    "current_loc":     {"type": "integer", "minimum": 100},
    "proposed_pattern":{"enum": ["service-layer", "selector", "dto", "query-object", "action", "custom-hook", "extract-helper", "split-by-domain"]},
    "target_loc":      {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 200},
    "coverage_or_plan":{"type": "string", "minLength": 5},
    "ai_context_savings_tokens": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0},
    "verdict":         {"enum": ["propose-extraction", "block-no-coverage", "block-pattern-not-applicable", "skip-already-small"]},
    "version":         {"type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"},
    "last_reviewed":   {"type": "string", "format": "date"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "fdp-order-views-py",
  "file_path": "src/orders/views.py",
  "framework": "django",
  "file_type": "view",
  "current_loc": 487,
  "proposed_pattern": "service-layer",
  "target_loc": 150,
  "coverage_or_plan": "tests/test_views.py (89% branch) + characterization plan in PR-4421",
  "ai_context_savings_tokens": 8500,
  "verdict": "propose-extraction",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "last_reviewed": "2026-05-23"
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "decomp",
  "file_path": "src/orders/views.py",
  "framework": "phoenix",
  "file_type": "thing",
  "current_loc": 60,
  "proposed_pattern": "service-layer",
  "target_loc": 800,
  "coverage_or_plan": "",
  "verdict": "propose-extraction",
  "version": "1.0",
  "last_reviewed": "today"
}
]]></code>
    <note>artefact_id missing fdp- prefix; framework not in enum; file_type not in enum; current_loc=60 below minimum (file isn't fat); target_loc=800 above max 200; coverage_or_plan empty; version + last_reviewed malformed.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <antipattern>
      <description>verdict=propose-extraction with coverage_or_plan empty.</description>
      <reason>Refactor without safety net = silent regression.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>framework=django + proposed_pattern=custom-hook (React-only pattern).</description>
      <reason>Pattern-framework mismatch; verdict block-pattern-not-applicable.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>target_loc &gt; current_loc.</description>
      <reason>Decomposition that makes the file bigger is not decomposition.</reason>
    </antipattern>
  </section>

  <reference path="templates/framework-decomposition-patterns.json">Schema canonical location.</reference>
  <reference path="scripts/validate-framework-decomposition-patterns.py">Validator that enforces this contract.</reference>
</text>
